snippet.title: Pennine ishtayo? | 4k | Short film | full movie | Sajin | Gopika anil | Achu sugandh
snippet.description:
Pennine Ishtayo - A Musical Short Film | Official Release
"Pennine Ishtayo" is a captivating Malayalam musical short film that explores the deep emotions of love, human connection, and the power of music. Directed by Achu Sugandh and produced by Nithin Thaivalappil under Filmika Cinemas, this film features powerful performances by Sajin Shiva, Gopika Anil, and an ensemble cast of talented actors. With stunning visuals by Rejin Santo and soul-stirring music composed by Bonny Louis, this film is sure to resonate with viewers of all ages.

From the mesmerizing vocals by Sadhika K R, Neethusha A C, Arjun, Nithin K Shiva, and Bonny Louis, to the skillful dance choreography by Surya R K, Pennine Ishtayi is a complete sensory experience that beautifully blends narrative and music.

Key Credits:

Written & Directed by: Achu Sugandh
Produced by: Nithin Thaivalappil, Filmika Cinemas
Cinematography (DoP): Rejin Santo
Music Director: Bonny Louis
Editor: Anandhu S Vijay
Sound Engineer: Aashif Ali
Colorist: Ebin Philip
Mix & Master: Arjun B Nair

Featuring:

Sajin Shiva
Gopika Anil
Vijaya Sadan
James Parackkal
Rahul
Sathwik
Milan Sandra
Fahad
Juman
Sarojini
Aasha
Aasha 2
Ottapalam Villagers
Special Guest Appearance: Mimmoos


*Music Credits*

Music Director : Bonny Louis

*Background score*
Composed & Produced  : Bonny Louis
Flute & Nadaswaram : Akhil Anil
Violin : Pious James
Vocals :Sadhika KR,  Neethusha AC, Arjun, Bonny
Recording Engineers: James Ullas, Arjun B Nair
Recorded @ Audio Miqueas &
Sonic Island 
Mix and Mastered By Arjun B Nair

*Kalyanam Song *

Music Composer : Bonny Louis
Singers : Nitin K Siva, Sadhika KR
Lyrics : Titto P Thankachan 
Chorus : Neethusha Ac, Bonny, Arjun , Sadhika
Keyboard Programmed : Emil Varghese
Guitars : Job Abraham 
Violin : Shimon Jasmine
Nadaswaram: Akhil Anil
Mix & Master : Arjun B Nair
Recorded @ Sonic Island by Arjun B Nair

*Kannulanja Song *

Music Composed & Produced : Bonny Louis 
Singer : Nitin K Siva 
Lyrics : Bonny Louis
Mix & Master : Arjun B Nair 
Recorded @ Sonic Island by Arjun B Nair


Dubbing & Mixing: Audio Notes, Ernakulam
Coloring: Studio HUE, Ernakulam

snippet.title: Worli Election Result: सुबह पीछे रहे Aaditya Thackeray Milind Deora जीते या हारे | वनइंडिया हिंदी
snippet.description:
महाराष्ट्र विधानसभा चुनाव 2024 (Worli Election Result) में महायुति को बंपर जीत मिली है. महायुति 226 तो एमवीए (MVA) महज 53 पर सिमटी हुई नजर आ रही है. वर्ली विधानसभा सीट पर शिवसेना यूबीटी के नेता आदित्य ठाकरे (Aaditya Thackeray) ने जीत दर्ज की है. आदित्य ने 81,000 वोट से मिलिंद देवड़ा (Milind Deora) को हराया है.

महाराष्ट्र विधानसभा चुनाव 2024 (Worli Election Result) में महायुति को बंपर जीत मिली है. महायुति 226 तो एमवीए (MVA) महज 53 पर सिमटी हुई नजर आ रही है. वर्ली विधानसभा सीट पर शिवसेना यूबीटी के नेता आदित्य ठाकरे (Aaditya Thackeray) ने जीत दर्ज की है. आदित्य ने 81,000 वोट से मिलिंद देवड़ा (Milind Deora) को हराया है.

snippet.description:

Buckle up for laughter, friendship, and a journey full of chaos in "Permission Na Milegi Dobara"! 🚗🎉
When Kritika discovers her late grandmother’s list of dying wishes, she decides to honor her legacy with a daring road trip to Mumbai. Joined by her two best friends, the trio embarks on a wild, female-only adventure to immerse her grandmother’s ashes in Mumbai’s sea.

snippet.title: Karnataka bypoll election result 2024: Congress wins all three seats
snippet.description:
The ruling Congress in Karnataka is jubilant after winning Legislative Assembly bypolls in all three constituencies of Channapatna, Shiggaon and Sandur

All three constituencies witnessed a direct fight between the Congress and Opposition BJP-JD(S) alliance. While the Congress wrested Channapatna and Shiggaon seats from the JD(S) and the BJP, respectively, it retained the Sandur seat.

With these results, the Congress tally in the Karnataka Assembly went up to 137.

snippet.title: Dhiktana Dhiktana - The Hustle Flip l Mad Trip  | MTV Hustle 4
snippet.description:
"This song is a reimagined version of the classic Bollywood track 'Dhiktana Dhiktana', transformed into a melancholic reflection on loneliness and disillusionment. By flipping the upbeat original into a somber tone, the song conveys the harsh reality that no one in this world truly belongs to you. It redefines the familiar melody to evoke a sense of sadness and introspection, making it a poignant commentary on isolation and unfulfilled connections.

Song Credits

Track Name: Dhiktana Dhiktana - The Hustle Flip
Written & Performed By: @MadTrip05 
Music Producer: Aditya Pushkarna
Primary Artist: @MadTrip05 
Track Name: Dhiktana Dhiktana - The Hustle Flip
Singer/Performed By/Cast: @MadTrip05 
Lyricist/Written By: @MadTrip05 
Music Produced By: Aditya Pushkarna
Co-Composer: Aditya Pushkarna
Music Label: Saregama
Genre: Hip Hop
Sub-Genre: Rap
Language:Hindi
Country of Origin/Source: India

👉 Follow us on X: https://x.com/kaanphodmusic?s=11 
👉 Follow us on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/kaanphodmusic/ 


Lyrics

Mad Trip@MadTrip05 

Kaisa hai tu kaise hain sab 
Poochhe khairiyat par dekhe haisiyat sab
pata chala sirf paison se rishte Hain
toh ab mere sirf paison se rishte hain

Haan maine jeet dekhi 
Haan maine  haar dekhi
Tedha bann ke chalna padta
Warna neki maar degi

Sadkon pe maar dekhi
Apno mein khaar dekhi
Qatl-e-aam ki khabrein Aksar 
qabrein toh aam dekhi

Dekhi saanp Seedhi
Baatein likhun saaf seedhi
Kisi ko bhi Sunn-ni nahi hai
Yahan pe meri aap beeti

Rishton mein rajneeti
Kisse bas jaydaad ke hisse na khaak mili
kishton mein haar mili

Dekhi Kitni shakal gayi pal mein Badal
mere Seene mein kyun hoti Har pal hulchul

Har pal chanchal mann karey bhag-dadd
Ab dil mera khaali Ghar lage khandar

Ghooma nahi main duniya  jahaanon mein kabhi 
Kyun ki pehle se hi maine dekh liya sab shayad
Bura waqt bhi dikha ke jaayega ek Jaadu 
Tu Khaali 10 tak ginn ho jayenge sab gayab

Ae khuda mujhe kya hua
Kyun lagta yeh begaana
Tu bataa main hoon kahan
Manzil ki raah dikhlana

Dhiktana dhiktana dhiktana
Yahan apno mein apna koi dikhta na
Dhiktana tiktana dhiktana
Saala sacchi mein saccha koi rishta na

Dhiktana dhiktana dhiktana
Yahan apno mein apna koi dikhta na
Dhiktana tiktana dhiktana
Saala sacchi mein saccha koi rishta na

Dhiktana tiktana dhiktana
Dhik dhiktana dhiktana dhiktana

Dhiktana dhiktana dhiktana
Dhik dhiktana dhiktana dhiktana

Aansu toh roz aaye par koi na ponchh paaye 
Bolun dil ki baatein par dil tak nahi yeh pahunch paaye
Dhokhe toh bahut khaaye woh toh roz ka hai 
Saare apna soche tu apno ka sochta hai kyun

doon main ghar walon ko dosh jo sochte mera roz
Afsos main unpe bojh main Kosta khud ko bahut
Jailon se bhi zyaada logon ke mann mein hai chor 
woh dekhe kab dheela ho naada 
kab kheenche langot

Jaana kahan soojhta bhi nahi
Ho Bhookhe paet nange paanv 
toh koi thookta bhi nahi
sawaal ka jawaab dene se baney crorepati
Lekin hum jaison ko yahan koi poochhta hi nahi

Bina taane khaaye  milti hain taaliyaan bhi na
Milti kaamyabi toh yeh dekhe khaamiyan bhi na

Kaafi ghalatiyan bhi Kari 
ghalati se seekha bhi main
Yeh duniya ek kitaab toh baatein kitaabi yeh
Chunautiyaan hain log hai kya ismein koi shaq
Roz bolun bhagwan se Enough is enough

Kaash Miley hote gham kam re
Humein bhi koi miley hote humdum re
Ghutt-te hain andar hi andar se
Ab Chubhte hain mujh ko yeh bandh kamre

Main So paaun kabhi chain se
Aise bhi din dikhlana 
Kho jaaunga bheed mein
Tu haath thaam lega na

Dhiktana tiktana dhiktana
Yahan apno mein apna koi dikhta na
Dhiktana tiktana  dhiktana
Saala sacchi mein saccha koi rishta na

Dhiktana tiktana dhiktana
Yahan apno mein apna koi dikhta na
Dhiktana tiktana dhiktana
Saala sacchi mein saccha koi rishta na

Apno ko dekha apno se ladte toh apna hai kaun aaya ek sawaal
Gairon ko dekha maine zakhmon ko bharte toh apna hai kaun phir aaya ek sawaal

snippet.title: New Thrower Troop, Firespitter Defense and Revive Spell in Clash of Clans!
snippet.description:
Town Hall 17 Update Sneak Peek2 brings a New Troop, Spell and Defense for Clash of Clans! The Helper Hut also brings the Lab Assistant to make your upgrades faster. Judo Sloth Gaming shares TH17 Gameplay of the Thrower Troop, Firespitter Defense and Revive Spell. All of these are explained so that you understand how they work, and the best strategies for them. This is only Sneak Peek 2 for the CoC November Update so be sure to subscribe for more Town Hall 17 content. The exact TH17 release date is not confirmed yet but it is typically shortly after sneak peeks and normally when Hammer Jam ends. Clash On!

Suggested Videos:
Sneak Peek 1 - Town Hall 17: https://youtu.be/jmUTOc4jUc4
100 Days Progress with the Gold Pass: https://youtu.be/CuMG4XUOr9I

Get Ready For The Biggest Blockbuster Flashing Worldwide 🔥! The Icon Star 'Allu Arjun' & the Dancing Queen 'Sreeleela' Is Coming to Rock The Floor!

Song Releasing on 24th Nov 2024. Stay Tuned!

Pushpa 2 - The Rule - Written and Directed by Sukumar. Produced by Naveen Yerneni and Y. Ravi Shankar of Mythri Movie Makers in association with Sukumar Writings. The film stars Allu Arjun, Fahadh Faasil, Rashmika Mandanna, Dhanunjay, Rao Ramesh, Sunil, Anasuya Bharadwaj & Ajay Ghosh. The film's music is composed by Devi Sri Prasad, with cinematography and editing performed by Miroslaw Kuba Brozek and Navin Nooli respectively.

Releasing in Cinemas on 5th December 2024💥😍🔥!

#Pushpa2TheRuleTrailer #AlluArjun #Pushpa2Trailer #Pushpa2TheRule #Sukumar #RashmikaMandanna #FahadhFaasil #DSP #MythriMovieMakers #Pushpa2 #Pushpa #Pushpa2Teaser #Pushpa2TheRuleGlimpse

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: Indians And Wedding Season | Ft. Tena Jaiin | The Paayal Jain
snippet.description:
Hey Guys 
The most awaited Wedding Video of the year is here , Enjoy this Shadi Season with this 🎉😍

Get HK Vitals Veg Collagen: https://bit.ly/3APi8bg
Marine Collagen : https://bit.ly/48Y7R9t
Use Code PJ10 for a special discount  🤩
Available in 5 fruity flavours 🍹

This Video shows all the crazy fun that happens in Big Fat Indian weddings. Indias and wedding season madness . Brides going on crazy diets to loose weight before Marriage , the morning after wedding and playing shadi rasam games with new bhahi and bhaiya like kagna games , Pre Bridal functions like mata ki choki , cocktail , sanjeet , roka , sagai , god tika , struggles of love marriage , cousins and best friends planning bachelorette for bride of the group , haldi ceremony and bhai behen getting emotional , Relatives giving advices about marriage. All the money , gifts , wedding preps , indian food , gol gappe , tikki , chart items , Paneer Tikka ,  spicy food , indian sweets , shaadi lehenga , bride makeup , wedding shopping , crazy dancing on wedding songs . Indian aunties taking lime light . Mehendi functions getting henna done and celebrating with family , friends , cousins . Ldki Wale vs ladke Wale , wedding photographers , pharo time and shadi wali coffee and crying on bidai , attending Big Fat Indian weddings like Kohli Tents , Flying Drones in weddings , Grand , Indian Bride entry with russians arounds , Wide variety of Indian Wedding Tasty food , malai chaap to gulab jamun , jalebi rabri , ice cream , Kids wearing skivi sweater under lehenga to deal with winter weddings , the struggles of Rishta before Marraige , Dealing with dowry , Every Girls struugles , Indian mom and super excited for daughter wedding , dreaming about grandchidlren , her beti being a maa one day , buying and placing a lot indian snacks daal kachori , samosa , pakore , dry fruits & nuts , barati ready for baraat dance on dhol , tired from 7 days of shadi functions , haldi , cocktail , sangeet , god tikka , mehendi , god bharai , halwai at home , indian relatives and theri demands , exclusive parlour makeup , hd bridal makeup , celebrity makeup , airbrush makeup , glitter makeup , high wedding makeup and hairstyle prices , wonder ladies with babies in wedding and doing rasams , dealing traffic jam while reaching a shaadi , every girls efforts of getting in lehenga , jhumka , doing makeup and then getting out of lehenga , removing heavy layers of makeup before sleeping , removing jwelery bangles , high heels , going on honeymoon and celebrating New Year goa , newyork , paris , london , switerland , enjoying bhaji , mathi achar , bondi ladoo , with tea or masala Chai , Going to Chandi Chowk for bridal shopping , choosing from wide variety of Bride lehenga color choices , red , maroon , pink , blue , green , trying different designs sabyasachi , manish malhotra , celebrity bridal lehengas , lehenga from jaipur with heavy embroidery work , crazy lehenga shopkeppers , high prices of lehenga and bargaining in that , bride not able to diet near marraige eating outside food golgappe to curb with full day of wedding shopping , after wedding counting money got from shagun , decorating gold daimond jewelry in front of indian guest buidling new homes before marraige , saas bahu happy in their new mother daughter relationship , kids mesmerized by new bhabhi and her makeup kit . 
This video is filled with such memories and situations we all have been in an indian wedding.  
Relish and Relive your Memories.. You will have major nostalgia .
Do share it with your friends , family , Relatives and Cousins .. A Very Happy New Year Guys

snippet.title: How To Train Your Dragon | Official Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
How To Train Your Dragon - In Theaters June 13

From three-time Oscar® nominee and Golden Globe winner Dean DeBlois, the creative visionary behind DreamWorks Animation’s acclaimed How to Train Your Dragon trilogy, comes a stunning live-action reimagining of the film that launched the beloved franchise. 
On the rugged isle of Berk, where Vikings and dragons have been bitter enemies for generations, Hiccup (Mason Thames; The Black Phone, For All Mankind) stands apart. The inventive yet overlooked son of Chief Stoick the Vast (Gerard Butler, reprising his voice role from the animated franchise), Hiccup defies centuries of tradition when he befriends Toothless, a feared Night Fury dragon. Their unlikely bond reveals the true nature of dragons, challenging the very foundations of Viking society. 

With the fierce and ambitious Astrid (BAFTA nominee Nico Parker; Dumbo, The Last of Us) and the village’s quirky blacksmith Gobber (Nick Frost; Snow White and the Huntsman, Shaun of the Dead) by his side, Hiccup confronts a world torn by fear and misunderstanding. 
As an ancient threat emerges, endangering both Vikings and dragons, Hiccup’s friendship with Toothless becomes the key to forging a new future. Together, they must navigate the delicate path toward peace, soaring beyond the boundaries of their worlds and redefining what it means to be a hero and a leader. 

The film also stars Julian Dennison (Deadpool 2), Gabriel Howell (Bodies), Bronwyn James (Wicked), Harry Trevaldwyn (Smothered), Ruth Codd (The Midnight Club), BAFTA nominee Peter Serafinowicz (Guardians of the Galaxy) and Murray McArthur (Game of Thrones).
How to Train Your Dragon is written, produced and directed by DeBlois. It is also produced by three-time Oscar® nominee Marc Platt (Wicked, La La Land) and Emmy winner Adam Siegel (Drive, 2 Guns). How To Train Your Dragon is part of the Filmed For IMAX® Program, which offers filmmakers IMAX® technology to help them deliver the most immersive movie experience to audiences around the world. 

Inspired by Cressida Cowell’s New York Times bestselling book series, DreamWorks Animation’s How to Train Your Dragon franchise has captivated global audiences, earning four Academy Award® nominations and grossing more than $1.6 billion at the global box-office. Now, through cutting-edge visual effects, DeBlois transforms his beloved animated saga into a breathtaking live-action spectacle, bringing the epic adventures of Hiccup and Toothless to life with jaw-dropping realism as they discover the true meaning of friendship, courage and destiny.

--------------------------------------------------------
Jethalal is thrilled after securing all the fridges. Soon after, a businessman visits Gada Electronics to close the deal. How will the transaction turn out?

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Sunn Mere Dil Episode 14 [Eng Sub] Digitally Presented by LUX - Happilac Paints and Ujooba Beauty Cream - Wahaj Ali - Maya Ali - 21st November 2024 - Har Pal Geo

Sunn Mera Dil Digitally Presented by LUX - Happilac Paints and Ujooba Beauty Cream

7th Sky Entertainment’s highly anticipated mega signature project, Sunn Mere Dil, is the most awaited drama serial. The mega drama boasts a star-studded cast led by Wahaj Ali and Maya Ali. Written by the renowned Khalil Ur Rehman Qamar and directed by the acclaimed Haseeb Hasan, Sunn Mere Dil promises to be a one-of-a-kind drama.

Sunn Mere Dil is a tale in which love finds a new meaning, where one person’s devotion quietly flourishes, often unnoticed. Their heart beats for someone who may never truly understand the depth of their feelings. Yet, in their silent sacrifices, they realize that true love is not about
possession but about selflessness.

Every unspoken gesture and unseen act of kindness brings them fulfillment, as they put their beloved’s happiness above their own, showing that love is not just about being together, it’s about redefining happiness, even at the expense of their contentment.

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Director: Haseeb Hasan
Writer: Khalil Ur Rehman Qamar

Cast:

Wahaj Ali as Bilal Abdullah 
Maya Ali as Sadaf
Usama Khan as Ammar
Hira Mani as Hamsha
Amar Khan as Dania
Saba Hameed as Farzana
Syed Mohammed Ahmed as Namdaar
Shahvir Kadwani as Zaviyaar

snippet.title: Arranged Marriage Episode - 3 | Living Together | Kavin Weds Nila | Vishnu Unnikrishnan | Sumathi
snippet.description:
#ArrangedMarriage #VishnuUnnikrishnan #ZeroFilter 

Arranged Marriage Episode 3 | Living Together | Kavin Weds Nila | Vishnu Unnikrishnan | Sumathi | Zero Filter

Welcome to Arranged Marriage, a heartfelt YouTube series that explores love found in the most unexpected way—through an arranged marriage! Follow the journey of two individuals brought together by family, tradition, and culture, who slowly discover friendship, trust, and eventually, love. Watch how their worlds collide and connect as they navigate new experiences, overcome misunderstandings, and learn what it means to truly love and respect each other.

In this episode, our beloved pair transitions from Coimbatore to Chennai to begin their fresh start as husband and wife. Watch how love, care, and a touch of possessiveness shape their relationship as they navigate new challenges, explore Chennai’s vibes, and strengthen their bond.

Each episode of Arranged Marriage delves into the beauty of growing affection and genuine connection, showcasing how relationships can blossom in surprising ways. If you enjoy stories of romance, personal growth, and cultural dynamics, subscribe and hit the notification bell for every chapter of this emotional and heartwarming tamil series.

Sunn Mere Dil Episode 13 [Eng Sub] Digitally Presented by LUX - Happilac Paints and Blesso Cosmetics - Wahaj Ali - Maya Ali - 20th November 2024 - Har Pal Geo

Sunn Mera Dil Digitally Presented by LUX - Happilac Paints and Blesso Cosmetics

7th Sky Entertainment’s highly anticipated mega signature project, Sunn Mere Dil, is the most awaited drama serial. The mega drama boasts a star-studded cast led by Wahaj Ali and Maya Ali. Written by the renowned Khalil Ur Rehman Qamar and directed by the acclaimed Haseeb Hasan, Sunn Mere Dil promises to be a one-of-a-kind drama.

Sunn Mere Dil is a tale in which love finds a new meaning, where one person’s devotion quietly flourishes, often unnoticed. Their heart beats for someone who may never truly understand the depth of their feelings. Yet, in their silent sacrifices, they realize that true love is not about
possession but about selflessness.

Every unspoken gesture and unseen act of kindness brings them fulfillment, as they put their beloved’s happiness above their own, showing that love is not just about being together, it’s about redefining happiness, even at the expense of their contentment.

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Director: Haseeb Hasan
Writer: Khalil Ur Rehman Qamar
